criteria.inclusion_criteria:
(1) Aged from 30 to 65 years, male and female; 
(2) the patients who suffer from bone un-union, bone defect or two or three segmental lumber spine disease requiring decompression surgery and intervertebral fusion;
(3) Be willing to sign the informed consent.

criteria.exclusion_criteria:
1. malignant or benign tumor; 
2. polycythemia vera;
3. myelodysplastic syndrome; 
4. infected disease; 
5. high dose chemoradiotherapy; 
6. blood system disease; 
7. operation site with infection or Hemoculture positive recently;
8. Hb＜7g/dl or severe coagulation disorders such as PT>10 seconds and platelet less than 60×10^9/L 
9. pregnant woman;
10. patients with decompensated cirrhosis,uremia or severe brain trauma; 
11. patient paticipating in other clinial trials in the same time.
